videos.headline: South Florida regains lead on 1-yard TD
videos.description: South Florida RB takes it in from one-yard out go give the Knights a 14-7 lead.

videos.headline: Dalvin Cook speeds down sideline for 75-yard score
videos.description: Florida State's Dalvin Cook busts through a pair of South Florida tackle attempts and speeds down the sideline for a 75-yard touchdown in the first quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Dalvin Cook speeds down sideline for 75-yard score) 2016/09/24

videos.headline: D. Francois pass to A. Tate for 39 yds to put Florida State in USF territory
videos.description: Deondre Francois pass complete to Auden Tate for 39 yds to the SFla 22 for a 1ST down

videos.headline: Cook's second TD ties game
videos.description: Florida State RB Dalvin Cook scores from 13 yards out to tie the game with South Florida at 14.

videos.headline: Stevenson's one-yard TD puts FSU in front
videos.description: Florida State FB Freddie Stevenson takes it in from one-yard out to give Florida State a 21-14 lead over South Florida.

videos.headline: Francois hits Wilson for 13-yard TD
videos.description: Florida State QB Deondre Francois connects with Jesus Wilson for a 13-yard touchdown to give the Seminoles a 28-14 lead over South Florida.

videos.headline: Dalvin Cook breaks free for 46-yard gain
videos.description: Florida State RB Dalvin Cook's big day continues with a 46-yard run in the second quarter against South Florida.

videos.headline: Q. Flowers pass intercepted by T. McFadden
videos.description: Quinton Flowers pass intercepted Tarvarus McFadden return for no gain to the FlaSt 47

videos.headline: FSU FB scores second TD of game
videos.description: Florida State FB Freddie Stevenson scores his second TD of the game to put the Seminoles up 38-14 on South Florida.

videos.headline: Q. Flowers pass intercepted by N. Andrews
videos.description: Quinton Flowers pass intercepted Nate Andrews return for no gain to the FlaSt 5

videos.headline: J. Patrick run for 2 yds for a TD
videos.description: Jacques Patrick run for 2 yds for a TD

videos.headline: South Florida RB Johnson scores from 24 yards out
videos.description: South Florida RB D'Ernest Johnson takes it in from 24 yards out to cut the Florida State lead to 45-21.

videos.headline: D. Johnson run for 4-yard TD
videos.description: D'Ernest Johnson run for 4 yds for a TD

videos.headline: Francois puts game out of reach with 35-yard TD run
videos.description: Florida State QB Deondre Francois races through South Florida's defense up the field for a 35-yard touchdown run, giving the Seminoles a 55-28 lead over South Florida.
